      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Every designer claims to be global these days. But will Diane Von Furstenberg play in Havana? We sent the planet's best-traveled photographers on assignment: shoot an iconic person in an iconic location. Here's how the looks fit with the landscape.</p>
